指令:rereg~n描述:重新注册人物~n例子:rereg
指令:look [目标名称] [目标序号]~n描述:观察当前场景或场景里的人物或物件~n~n例子:~n观察场景: look / l / 5~n观察当前场景第一个人物或物件:~nlook dog / look dog 1~n观察当前场景非第一个人物或物件:~nlook dog n (n > 1)
en: COMMAND:look [target name] [target sequence]~nDESCRIPTION:Observe current scene, or target character or item in current scene~n~nEXAMPLE:~nObserve scene: look / l / 5~nObserve the first character or item in current scene:~nlook dog / look dog 1~nObserve non-first character or item in current scene:~nlook dog n (n > 1)

en: COMMAND:perform [skill name] on [target name]~nDESCRIPTION:Perform skill attack on someone.~n~n例子:perform attack on dog
